description:
Danny welcomes Chris Baker (@BakerseeBakerdo) to recap this week's Real Housewives of Orange County. Danny also chats with the beautiful Stephanie Hollman from The Real Housewives of Dallas about opening up about her past on the show, her home spa, her relationships with the other women on the show, and more.


#RHOC Recap: 8:15

#RHOD/Stephanie Hollman Interview: 45:44
